# Business Insights

## Key Findings

### 1. Best Performing AI Model
GPT Assist Pro achieved the highest accuracy score among all AI models.

### 2. High Escalation Areas
Login and account-related issues required the highest human escalation.

### 3. Customer Satisfaction
Users with lower chatbot sentiment scores were more likely to escalate tickets.

### 4. Revenue Contribution
Premium and Enterprise users contributed most of the platform revenue.

### 5. Support Efficiency
Most resolved tickets were closed within a few hours.

## Recommendations

- Improve chatbot handling for login/account issues.
- Reduce response time for high-priority tickets.
- Increase focus on premium customer retention.
- Enhance AI training using escalation cases.
